                    <span id="c-1101077587" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1101077587" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1101077587">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44589582/">竹去</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-10-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">因为一贯接受的宣传，没怎么看过胡适的书，这本是个惊喜，记的生活琐事，能看出来胡适的博学、严谨、真诚。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1077047628">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1077047628" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1077047628" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1077047628">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linfeil90/">李墨猪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-08-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读这书，拿骆玉明老师的话来印证再合适不过了：胡适之是一个漂亮的人。胡适对具体问题的见解，现在也许只剩了学术史或思想史的价值。但对胡适其人，至今想望其风采。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="957649871">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-957649871" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-957649871" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="957649871">有用</a>
